#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Konsole is an X terminal emulator, often referred to as a terminal or a "
#| "shell. It emulates a command line interface in a text only window."
msgid ""
"Konsole is a terminal to run a command shell. It provides a command line "
"interface for directly controlling your computer."
msgstr ""
"Konsole je emulator terminala za X, koji se često naziva samo terminalom ili "
"školjkom. Emulira sučelje komandne linije u čisto tekstualnom prozoru."

